Path: Nushell
Content:
waywardmonkeys 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3757] updated s3handler to 0.7 (really 0.7.3).
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3747] updated wasm sample gitignore for node_modules.
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3742] simplified 
``is_executable``
 in 
``nu-completion``
.
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3741] removed ptree dep from nu-command, remove associated feature.
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3739] updated minus, tui to remove crossterm 0.18 dep.
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3732] removed empty 
``trace``
 feature.
mcbattirola created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3754] #3385: Add unique option for uniq command
efx 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3753] ported strings size engine-p (#3690)
fdncred created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3752] a few things that make it easier to debug keybindings
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3749] added a couple more features
, fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3745] ^ls doesn't exist on windows
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3743] tried to use regular trim commands as much as possible
yaymukund 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3751] removed outdated note in README.md.
jonathandturner 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3750] fixed nothing string comparison
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3729] fixed a Wasm issue
kubouch 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3740] downgraded crossterm to fix pager compilation
therealprof 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3724] bumped a few source compatible nu-command dependencies
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3723] bumped rand version used by nu-command to 0.8
elferherrera created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3722] a new take command for dataframes
